      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下结构：Code和Audit都指向Define，Define指向Barg；Bail也指向Barg，同时Barg还要指回Bail形成闭环？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Audit",
        "Define",
        "Bail",
        "Barg"
